# --- Rust build artifacts ---
# Workspace root, the excluded standalone crates (unstation-chain, unstation-session),
# the Tauri app, and the fuzz crate all produce their own target/ dirs.
/target
crates/*/target
desktop/src-tauri/target
crates/unstation-core/fuzz/target
crates/unstation-core/fuzz/corpus
crates/unstation-core/fuzz/artifacts
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# --- Node / web ---
node_modules/
dist/
*.tsbuildinfo

# --- Secrets & environment ---
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Editors & OS ---
.DS_Store
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp

# --- Logs & scratch ---
*.log
/scratch/
/tmp/

# --- Docs site ---
# Generated static output of docs/build.py (published by the Pages workflow; never committed).
docs/_site/

# --- Local design docs ---
# Internal specs, research, and notes stay local; only the README and the curated
# public docs site (docs/, published to GitHub Pages) are tracked.
*.md
!README.md
!docs/index.md
!docs/how-it-works.md
!docs/protocol.md
!docs/engineering.md
!docs/security.md
!docs/faq.md
!docs/run-a-relay.md
!docs/contributing.md

# Local cross-builds of the seed binary (Docker; see crates/unstation-node/README.md)
/target-linux-*
/dist-seed
